trans-unit.source: Provides a base class for getting and setting option values for a designer.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en basisklasse for henting og angivelse av verdiene for en designer.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerOptionService class provides a collection of options.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DesignerOptionService inneholder en samling av alternativene.

trans-unit.source: Each of these option collections has an indexer that enables it to be further filtered.
trans-unit.target: Hvert enkelt av disse alternativet samlingene har en indekserer som gjør det mulig å filtreres videre.

trans-unit.source: Each option collection contains its own set of options, as well as a rollup of all of its child options.
trans-unit.target: Hver alternativet-samlingen inneholder sitt eget sett med alternativer, i tillegg til en samling av alle underordnede alternativene.

trans-unit.source: In the event of a naming conflict between properties, the outermost options object takes precedence.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det oppstår en naming konflikt mellom egenskaper du ytterste alternativer objektet prioriteres.

trans-unit.source: The following **Tools | Options** user interface (UI) structure shows how the outermost options object takes on greater importance: **WindowsFormsDesigner | General** - **SnapToGrid** - **ShowGrid** - **GridSize** Given a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerOptionService> named `service`, to get to the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ParentControlDesigner.GridSize%2A> property, you would make the following call: [!code-cs[IDesignerOptionServiceExample#2](~/add/codesnippet/csharp/t-system.componentmodel._122_1.cs)] [!code-vb[IDesignerOptionServiceExample#2](~/add/codesnippet/visualbasic/t-system.componentmodel._122_1.vb)] [!code-cpp[IDesignerOptionServiceExample#2](~/add/codesnippet/cpp/t-system.componentmodel._122_1.cpp)] This works, until you want to move <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ParentControlDesigner.GridSize%2A> to another page.
trans-unit.target: Følgende **verktøy | Alternativene** bruker brukergrensesnittet (UI) strukturen viser hvordan ytterste alternativer objektet finner på større Viktighet: **WindowsFormsDesigner | Generell** - **SnapToGrid** - **ShowGrid** - **GridSize** gitt en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerOptionService>navnet `service`til å hente verdien for den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ParentControlDesigner.GridSize%2A>-egenskapen, kan du gjøre følgende kall: [!code-cs [IDesignerOptionServiceExample&2;](~/add/codesnippet/csharp/t-system.componentmodel._122_1.cs)][!code-vb[IDesignerOptionServiceExample&2;](~/add/codesnippet/visualbasic/t-system.componentmodel._122_1.vb)][!code-cpp[IDesignerOptionServiceExample&2;](~/add/codesnippet/cpp/t-system.componentmodel._122_1.cpp) ] dette fungerer, før du ønsker å flytte <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ParentControlDesigner.GridSize%2A>til en annen side.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ParentControlDesigner.GridSize%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.ParentControlDesigner.GridSize%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerOptionService>

trans-unit.source: Also, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerOptionService> provides no discovery mechanism.
If you do not know what string to pass in, the service cannot find the property value.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke vet hva streng skal sendes i, finner ikke tjenesten egenskapsverdien.

trans-unit.source: The DesignerOptionService class addresses these issues.

You can query collections, and there is a type converter defined on the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerOptionService.DesignerOptionCollection> object that marks the collection as expandable.
trans-unit.target: Du kan spørre samlinger, og det er en type konverteringsprogram som er definert i den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerOptionService.DesignerOptionCollection>objekt som merker samlingen som utvides.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerOptionService.DesignerOptionCollection>

trans-unit.source: With this type converter, you can pass the entire designer option service to a property window and visually inspect the service.
trans-unit.target: Med denne typen konverteringsprogram kan du sende hele designer alternativet-tjenesten til et egenskapen og inspisere visuelt tjenesten.
